tarefas.prompt:
Leia o arquivo ../orchestration/context.md para entender o projeto.

Crie os types TypeScript e o API client do frontend.

Crie **src/types/subject.ts**:
- Subject: { id: number; title: string; description: string | null; status: 'pending' | 'processing' | 'completed' | 'error'; totalLessons: number; processedLessons: number; createdAt: string }
- Lesson: { id: number; youtubeUrl: string; youtubeTitle: string | null; durationSeconds: number | null; status: 'pending' | 'transcribing' | 'transcribed' | 'error'; transcriptMethod: 'youtube' | 'whisper' | null; orderIndex: number }
- SubjectDetail: Subject & { lessons: Lesson[] }
- CreateSubjectInput: { title: string; description?: string; youtubeUrls: string[] }
- ProcessingStatus: { subjectId: number; status: string; totalLessons: number; processedLessons: number; currentStep: string; lessons: { id: number; status: string; youtubeTitle: string | null }[] }

Crie **src/types/content.ts**:
- StudyPlan: { id: number; subjectId: number; content: string; createdAt: string }
- Summary: { id: number; lessonId: number; youtubeTitle: string; content: string; keyTopics: string[]; createdAt: string }
- QuizQuestion: { id: number; lessonId: number | null; question: string; options: string[]; correctIndex: number; explanation: string; difficulty: 'easy' | 'medium' | 'hard' }
- ExamRadarItem: { id: number; lessonId: number | null; topic: string; relevance: 'high' | 'medium' | 'low'; professorQuote: string | null; reasoning: string }
- QuizAttempt: { id: number; totalQuestions: number; correctAnswers: number; percentage: number; createdAt: string }
- QuizAttemptInput: { totalQuestions: number; correctAnswers: number; answers: { quizId: number; selectedIndex: number; correct: boolean }[] }

Crie **src/api/client.ts**:
- Criar instância axios com baseURL 'http://localhost:3001/api'
- Exportar api

Crie **src/api/subjects.ts**:
- getSubjects(): GET /subjects → data
- getSubject(id): GET /subjects/:id → data
- createSubject(input): POST /subjects → data
- deleteSubject(id): DELETE /subjects/:id
- getProcessingStatus(id): GET /subjects/:id/status → data

Crie **src/api/content.ts**:
- getStudyPlan(subjectId): GET /subjects/:id/study-plan → data
- getSummaries(subjectId): GET /subjects/:id/summaries → data (retorna .data do response)
- getQuizzes(subjectId): GET /subjects/:id/quizzes → data (retorna .data do response)
- getExamRadar(subjectId): GET /subjects/:id/exam-radar → data (retorna .data do response)
- submitQuizAttempt(subjectId, input): POST /subjects/:id/quiz-attempts → data
- getQuizAttempts(subjectId): GET /subjects/:id/quiz-attempts → data (retorna .data do response)

Todas as funções de API devem importar api de './client' e usar tipagem correta nos retornos.

NÃO crie componentes nem hooks.
